**StreamTunnelScope**  
**Description:**  
Smoothly visualizes high-frequency data streams in a real-time tunnel view with optional peak markers.

```markdown
# StreamTunnelScope - Realtime Data Stream Viewer

StreamTunnelScope displays scrolling charts of numeric input with minimal delay and customizable pacing.

## Features
- Live scrollable graph  
- Peak/valley detection  
- Matplotlib backend

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/StreamTunnelScope.git
cd StreamTunnelScope
python visualize.py
